eam.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center"><button class="bg-indigo-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors font-medium">Start free trial</button><a href="#pricing" class="bg-gray-800 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors font-medium inline-block text-center">View pricing</a></div><div class="mt-16 relative"><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-indigo-700 rounded-xl h-64 md:h-96 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="text-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity mx-auto mb-4 opacity-80" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg><p class="text-white opacity-80">Real-time metrics visualization</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gray-50"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-16"><p class="text-indigo-600 font-medium mb-2">Why Pulseboard</p><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Built for teams that already drowned in dashboards.</h2></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200"><div class="bg-indigo-100 w-14 h-14 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity text-indigo-600" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Live signal, not stale charts</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Every metric is a real-time stream. No 24-hour delay, no nightly batch jobs, no &quot;last refreshed&quot; disclaimer.</p></div><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200"><div class="bg-indigo-100 w-14 h-14 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target text-indigo-600" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">One number per goal</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Each team picks the single metric that defines success this quarter. Pulseboard makes that number unmissable.</p></div><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200"><div class="bg-indigo-100 w-14 h-14 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap text-indigo-600" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Wired into your stack</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Drop-in SDKs for Node, Python, Go, and Rust. Send an event in 30 seconds, see it on the board immediately.</p></div><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200"><div class="bg-indigo-100 w-14 h-14 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/20